OL,3,CWales' poverty crisis deepening with
OL,4,C'little progress' in 20 years, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FPoverty in Wales is deepening,
OL,8,Faccording to a new report from the
OL,9,FJoseph Rowntree Foundation (JRF) and
OL,10,Fthe Bevan Foundation.
OL,12,FThe study also claims there has been
OL,13,Flittle progress in reducing poverty in
OL,14,FWales over the past 20 years, with
OL,15,Fpoverty rates remaining at around
OL,16,F21`22%.
