OL,3,CWales' poverty crisis deepening with
OL,4,C'little progress' in 20 years, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHouseholds below 50% of the median
OL,8,Fhousehold income are defined as living
OL,9,Fin deep poverty and those living below
OL,10,F40% are defined as being in very deep
OL,11,Fpoverty.
OL,13,FDr Victoria Winckler, Director at the
OL,14,FBevan Foundation, said: "It is
OL,15,Fshocking that there has been no
OL,16,Fprogress reducing poverty in Wales in
OL,17,Fthe last twenty years.
