OL,3,CWales' poverty crisis deepening with
OL,4,C'little progress' in 20 years, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Even worse, more people are in deep
OL,8,Fpoverty than ever before, forced to
OL,9,Fuse food banks, unable to heat their
OL,10,Fhomes, watching every penny.
OL,12,F"The report shows that the root causes
OL,13,Fare many years of cuts to social
OL,14,Fsecurity coupled with a severe
OL,15,Fshortage of decent jobs and affordable
OL,16,Fhousing. The steps taken by the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment to alleviate poverty are
OL,18,Fwelcome, but there is much more to do.
