OL,3,CWales' poverty crisis deepening with
OL,4,C'little progress' in 20 years, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"As political parties gear up for the
OL,8,Fnext Senedd election, we urge them to
OL,9,Fcommit to practical, deliverable
OL,10,Faction to end poverty."
OL,12,FChris Birt, JRF Associate Director for
OL,13,FScotland, Wales, and Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fsaid: "Deepening poverty and a child
OL,15,Fpoverty rate of almost one in three in
OL,16,FWales should be a stark wake up call
OL,17,Fto both the UK Government and all
OL,18,Fparties aspiring to form the next
OL,19,FWelsh Government.
