OL,3,CWales' poverty crisis deepening with
OL,4,C'little progress' in 20 years, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"But the scale of the challenge needs
OL,8,Fto be met by the scale of the
OL,9,Fresponse. The same is of course true
OL,10,Fof the UK Government. The threadbare
OL,11,Fsocial security system is their
OL,12,Fresponsibility, and it drives much
OL,13,Fhardship. A good place to start
OL,14,Freversing that would be casting the
OL,15,Ftwo-child limit into history as
OL,16,Fquickly as possible.
